g.title: j2805085341
g.text: Quincy came to me and said the absolutely strangest thing. That you wanted to talk to me... about your 'feelings?'

g.title: j393926521
g.text: I really just wanted to apologize for the terrible things I said.

g.title: j3864229681
g.text: I just wanted to tell you that I have feelings for you.

g.title: j3716896249
g.text: Well... seems like a poor choice for me to hold a grudge given our situation. If you mean it? I forgive you.

g.title: j554508632
g.text: And... truth be told? I can't help but admit that I've been harbouring some feelings for you...

g.title: j4283710753
g.text: And I would be keen to remind you that you had your chance.

g.title: j3980348580
g.text: And why have you kept this to yourself until now?

g.title: j4098741761
g.text: If you're serious about wanting to give 'this' a go, between us? I'd be willing to do the same.

g.title: j4191728704
g.text: But I'd also be lying if I didn't admit that I missed you and would be willing to give this another go, if you were.

g.title: j2802548246
g.text: Maybe I've been confused on how this all works.

g.title: j2232079257
g.text: Seems so. Well. If you'd like to give 'this' a go, I would be more than happy to.
